title: Literary landmarks of Edinburgh,
author: Hutton, Laurence
snippet: It is to be inferred that this is ajoke whichgot into the head of one Scotchman without a surgical operation. John Home was born on the east side of QualityStreet, near Bernard Street, Leith, in a house nolonger standing. He was educated in the grammar-school of his native town, and at the University ofEdinburgh.
